<item>
            <title>[PIG-2010] Bundle registered jars via distributed cache</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2010</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently registered jars get collapsed into a single job megajar that gets submitted to Hadoop.&lt;br/&gt;
A better pattern would be to take advantage of the distributed cache.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
